<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">Strategy</p>
<h1>Target Audience Analysis – the Foundation of a Customer-Oriented Online Shop</h1>
<p>Target audience analysis serves to identify current market developments in your industry. This enables you to respond to changes with strategic planning and customer-oriented implementation of your campaigns. Our task in the analysis is to filter out target groups with strong appeal to your business model, assign their purchasing behaviour and adapt the functionality of your online shop to these habits.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>Target Audience Analysis by Hob by Horse with High-Performance Technology Concepts</h2>
<p>Before the target audience analysis, we create a definition protocol from existing shop data. Age, hobbies and profession play a role here, for example. Once these are summarised into a value concept for the customer groups, we analyse possible purchasing motives, influencers, preferences, brand preferences and, for regular customers, the purchase frequency. The actual methodology only begins at the end of this analysis. Content created now is characterised by high conversion strength and relevance for this target group.</p>
<h2>Target Audience Analysis for Better Assessment of Visitors</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Online research:</strong> It allows for a quick analysis supplementary to other analysis methods. The sources used are less precise in terms of credibility, but can be utilised to a high percentage with the tracking tool Google Analytics.</li>
<li><strong>Interviews:</strong> They require more effort from you and customers than other methods, but deliver representative results of high personal significance as a practical example. Even interviews with a small customer base lead to valuable insights for possible process optimisations.</li>
<li><strong>Surveys:</strong> They can be offered anonymously to all visitors of your online shop. For survey creation, we develop simple templates whose questions can be clearly answered (yes/no, smiley method, star rating etc.) by your visitors. Advantageous is the potentially high number of participants and thus a strong significance with little error potential for a large market share of your industry in e-commerce.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Interesting Industries for Target Audience Analysis</h2>
<p>To understand the purchasing behaviour of different customer groups, target audience analysis determines not only personal purchasing behaviour, but also industry-specific search and selection habits of wholesalers and retailers in manufacturing and processing industries, import and export, the fashion industry or automotive industry. Adjustment is needed in the A2A or A2C area, where authorities trade services and products with each other or make them available to private visitors. Particularly versatile and changeable are the purchasing habits in the fashion industry with its constantly changing trends and the large lifestyle sector.</p>
<h2>Benefits of Target Audience Analysis by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>B2B target audience analysis meets a specialist trade audience. These visitors appreciate online shops with high information content and place less value on flowery advertising claims. B2C target groups shop much more emotionally. They are happy to be seduced into impulse purchases by witty storytelling or promising advertising presentations. Manufacturers position themselves on the D2C market through meaningful presentations of product launches and benefits. The A2C target group is often overlooked – but here too, potential customers seek online shops with the best-explained products and most easily managed services.</p>
<p><em>Would you like to better position your marketing campaigns and create an optimal shopping experience for your target group through target audience analysis? Call Hob by Horse or arrange a consultation appointment by <a href="mailto:info@hob-by-horse.de">email</a>!</em></p>
